metadata.name: Pluteus Artemis
metadata.description: DMT Gods is a collection of deities celebrating the harmonious and benevolent energy of the spirit molecule. A naturally occurring psychoactive compound found in nearly every living organism on Earth and possibly the universe. DMT Gods represent a community of molecular relationships interacting across multidimensional spheres that bind all living things together through plants, animals, the earth and human consciousness. Explore the relationships between Gods via metadata and become part of the story by visiting  https://hipworth.studio/dmtgods/
